🌱 Very Easy / Foundation (Basics of Tree Traversals & Structure)

Start with these to get comfortable with recursion, DFS, and BFS.

✅ 104. Maximum Depth of Binary Tree – Basic recursion / DFS.

✅ 100. Same Tree – Compare two trees node by node.

✅ 101. Symmetric Tree – Mirror check using recursion / queue.

✅ 226. Invert Binary Tree – Swap left and right recursively.

✅ 617. Merge Two Binary Trees – Build intuition on combining subtrees.

✅ 700. Search in a Binary Search Tree – Basic BST property.

✅ 701. Insert into a Binary Search Tree – Recursively insert.

🌿 Easy Binary Tree Problems (Classic Traversals + Simple Patterns)

These help you practice preorder, inorder, postorder, and BFS.

✅ 94. Binary Tree Inorder Traversal – Recursion + stack version.

✅ 144. Binary Tree Preorder Traversal – Same pattern.

✅ 145. Binary Tree Postorder Traversal – Classic recursion.

✅ 102. Binary Tree Level Order Traversal – BFS with queue.

✅ 107. Binary Tree Level Order Traversal II – Reverse BFS order.

✅ 199. Binary Tree Right Side View – BFS/DFS trick.

✅ 111. Minimum Depth of Binary Tree – Similar to max depth but careful with nulls.

✅ 112. Path Sum – Root-to-leaf recursion check.

🌳 Medium Binary Tree Problems (Structural Thinking)

Now move into subtree problems, tree construction, and recursive logic.

✅ 105. Construct Binary Tree from Preorder and Inorder Traversal – Important!

✅ 106. Construct Binary Tree from Inorder and Postorder Traversal

✅ 654. Maximum Binary Tree – Build using divide and conquer.

✅ 236. Lowest Common Ancestor of a Binary Tree (LCA) – Key recursion concept.

✅ 230. Kth Smallest Element in a BST – Inorder traversal property.

✅ 98. Validate Binary Search Tree – Recursive range check.

✅ 173. Binary Search Tree Iterator – Inorder traversal with stack.

✅ 450. Delete Node in a BST – Harder BST manipulation.

✅ 129. Sum Root to Leaf Numbers – DFS with number accumulation.

✅ 113. Path Sum II – Collect all valid root-to-leaf paths.

✅ 222. Count Complete Tree Nodes – Uses binary search + height.

✅ 257. Binary Tree Paths – Generate all root-to-leaf paths.

🌲 Hard Binary Tree Problems (Advanced Recursion + DP on Trees)

These involve combining recursion results, dynamic programming, or tricky conditions.

🔥 124. Binary Tree Maximum Path Sum – Classic hard recursion DP.

🔥 297. Serialize and Deserialize Binary Tree – BFS/DFS + string encoding.

🔥 968. Binary Tree Cameras – Greedy + recursion states.

🔥 337. House Robber III – DP on trees (choose or skip node).

🔥 1457. Pseudo-Palindromic Paths in a Binary Tree – Bitmask + DFS.

🔥 99. Recover Binary Search Tree – Detect swapped nodes in BST.

🔥 530. Minimum Absolute Difference in BST – Inorder property.

🔥 652. Find Duplicate Subtrees – Serialization + hashing.

🔥 987. Vertical Order Traversal of a Binary Tree – BFS + sorting.

🔥 863. All Nodes Distance K in Binary Tree – Parent pointer + BFS.

